+
+Today's sky: ${topAlignments || 'no major alignments'}.
+Personal transits: ${topTransits || 'none exact today'}.
+Moon phase: ${moonPhase.phase} (${moonPhase.percentage}% illuminated).
+Personal day number: ${personalDayNumber}.
